        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">BridgeInstallation</rdfs:label>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">A BridgeInstallation is a permanent part of a Bridge (inside and/or outside) which does not have the significance of a BridgePart. In contrast to BridgeConstructiveElements, a BridgeInstallation is not essential from a structural point of view. Examples are stairs, antennas or railways.</skos:definition>
    </owl:Class>
    


