        <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">Building</rdfs:label>
        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">A Building is a free-standing, self-supporting construction that is roofed, usually walled, and can be entered by humans and is normally designed to stand permanently in one place. It is intended for human occupancy (e.g. a place of work or recreation), habitation and/or shelter of humans, animals or things.</skos:definition>
    </owl:Class>
    


