        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">A BuildingUnit is a logical subdivision of a Building. BuildingUnits are formed according to some homogeneous property like function, ownership, management, or accessibility. They may be separately sold, rented out, inherited, managed, etc.</skos:definition>
    </owl:Class>
    


